Package: crimeTools
Type: Package
Title: Data Analysis and Visualization Tools for Crime Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Reinhold Melcher
Maintainer: Reinhold Melcher <reinhold.melcher@freenet.de>
Description: crimeTools is a package designed to make analysis and visualization of crime survey data straightforward by providing high-level functions for the most common chart types.
    crimeTools builds on the R packages survey and srvyr to properly weight the results in accordance with the survey and sampling design.
